Robert Kirkman's Secret History of Comics - Season 1 - Episode 2 (WEB-DL - MP4)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The Walking Dead comic book creator Robert Kirkman stars in this documentary
series that takes a deeper look into the stories, people and events that have
transformed the world of comic books. It also features interviews with icons
such as Stan Lee, Patty Jenkins, Lynda Carter, Kevin Smith, Famke Janssen,
J.K. Simmons, Michelle Rodriguez, and Todd McFarlane, among many others.

Produced by Skybound Entertainment and AMC Studios.


As comic books became popular and male superheroes rose to stardom, one man
created a feminist superhero inspired by both his wife and his mistress.
